@startuml
title Plugin Theme Lifecycle Sequence

actor User
participant "Plugins Manager UI" as UI
participant "Renderer API" as API
participant "Main ThemeManager" as TM
database "Global Plugins Path" as GP

User -> UI : Add/Update theme plugin
UI -> API : request load plugin theme
API -> TM : loadPluginTheme(path)
TM -> GP : read theme.json
GP --> TM : theme payload
TM -> TM : merge with base theme
TM --> API : merged theme
API --> UI : update-theme event
UI --> User : theme applied

@enduml
